***
*** LOADING MODULES
***

load ./falcon.maude

***
*** SEARCH
***

*** Signature search on init1
search init1 =>! {SSS:SamplePool}<(ID1:Identifier[KS1:Set{Key}](mIv(ID2:Identifier,STR:StringMSG), ATTS)) PS:Principals >net(MSGS:Msgs) such that ID1:Identifier =/= ID2:Identifier .
*** Key recovery attack on init1

*** Signature search on init2
search init2 =>! {SSS:SamplePool}<(ID1:Identifier[KS1:Set{Key}](mIv(ID2:Identifier,STR:StringMSG), ATTS)) PS:Principals >net(MSGS:Msgs) such that ID1:Identifier =/= ID2:Identifier .
*** Key recovery attack on init2

***
*** MODEL CHECKING
***

load model-checker.maude
load ./falcon-PREDS.maude
load ./falcon-CHECK.maude

*** TERMINATION
red modelCheck(init1, [] (wantsToSignAndSendTo(Alice, Bob) -> <> verifiedSignatureFrom(Bob, Alice))) .

*** FAIRNESS
---red modelCheck(init1, [] (wantsToSignAndSendTo(Alice, Bob) -> [] (<> verifiedSignatureFrom(Bob, Alice)))) .

